I installed the fim image viewer for viewing images in the terminal
sudo apt install fim
to open any image using fim --> fim -a <image_name>
to quit fim --> q or Esc key
image navigation --> PageUp & PageDown or Enter
zoom --> +/-
autoscale --> a
fitting width and height --> w/h
flip --> f
mirror --> m
rotate(clockwise) --> r
rotate(anti-clockwise) --> R
